dcterms:description: An in vivo dataset collected during a partial nephrectomy procedure using a da Vinci Si surgical system, consisting of 20,000 stereo pairs of rectified images sampled over 11 video sequences.
dcterms:title: In vivo dataset collected in a partial nephrectomy procedure

dcterms:description: Stereo videos collected during robotic partial nephrectomy, used for validation of the proposed depth estimation framework.
dcterms:title: Stereo videos collected in robotic partial nephrectomy

dcterms:description: A testing dataset consisting of 3000 stereo pairs of images used for evaluating the performance of the depth estimation models.
dcterms:title: Testing dataset of 3000 stereo pairs of images
